<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.7">
<l>miṉṉiṉ nuṇṇiṭai maṭakkoṭi kāraṇam vilaṅkaliṉ micaiyilaṅkai</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉ nīṇmuṭi poṭiceyta maintaṉa tiṭammaṇi varainīḻal</l>
<l>aṉṉa māmala raravintat tamaḷiyil peṭaiyoṭu miṉitamara</l>
<l>cenne lārkava rikkulai vīcutaṇ tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the man who, because of the simple creeper</l>
<l rend="indent">with a lightning-thin waist,</l>
<l>Made dust of the high crowns of the king of Lanka on a mountain top,</l>
<l>Is cool Tiruvayintirapuram where fan[-like] full clusters of red paddy sway,</l>
<l>As a swan settles sweetly with the hen in a bed of large lotus blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">in the shade on a sapphire hill.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
